{"thag2.16:0.1":"Theragatha 2.16 ","thag2.16:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.16:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag2.16:0.4":"Mahakalattheragatha ","thag2.16:1.1":"“Kali itthi brahati dhankarupa, ","thag2.16:1.2":"Satthinca bhetva aparanca satthim; ","thag2.16:1.3":"Bahanca bhetva aparanca baham, ","thag2.16:1.4":"Sisanca bhetva dadhithalakamva; ","thag2.16:1.5":"Esa nisinna abhisandahitva. ","thag2.16:2.1":"Yo ve avidva upadhim karoti, ","thag2.16:2.2":"Punappunam dukkhamupeti mando; ","thag2.16:2.3":"Tasma pajanam upadhim na kayira, ","thag2.16:2.4":"Maham puna bhinnasiro sayissan”ti. ","thag2.16:2.5":"… Mahakalo thero …. "}